===Plant Petiole Nitrate Test Instructions===
Use this kit to test for nitrate levels in plants and hone in on appropriate fertilizer application.  Test corn and cotton stalks or the sap from petioles of leafy crops to monitor nitrate level fluctuations.  For best results, refer to a Certified Crop Advisor for plant sampling advice.  Refer to the Petiole Sap Nitrate Guidelines under Related Information for testing crop petioles.

This kit will detect 0 ppm - 1000 ppm Nitrate-N.  (1000 ppm Nitrate-N = 5000 ppm Nitrate)

